description: Use "." not ":" for delimiters in names
alwaysApply: true
---

# Delimiters

Use **`.`** (dot) as the delimiter, never `:` (colon).

- Script names: `dev.local`, `db.push.local`, `test.watch` — not `dev:local`, `db.push:local`, `test:watch`
- Other compound names: prefer `foo.bar` over `foo:bar`
